Image Prompt:
Create an ethereal and symbolic representation of Christ's two natures, combining elements of divinity and humanity in a visually striking way. Depict a figure that embodies both the transcendence of God and the earthly presence of Jesus, surrounded by celestial light and earthly elements, conveying the profound mystery of the Incarnation. Incorporate subtle visual cues such as a halo and human features intertwined with cosmic symbols to represent the dual nature of Christ in a captivating and reverent manner.
